## .NET Performance Analysis: CaseTransformExtensions.cs

### Scan Execution Checklist

| Recipe | Hits |
|--------|------|
| `.ToLower()`/`.ToUpper()` without culture | 2 |
| `.Substring(` calls | 2 (same line) |
| `RegexOptions.Compiled` | 7 |
| `[GeneratedRegex]` | 3 ✅ |
| `new Regex(` (per-instance) | 1 |
